Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's invite our Special Bomby Guest for today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, today's guest is by all measures truly a top star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A super popular woman in her 20s
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- In her 20s?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since her teens she's been doing music, dramas, and CMs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very active
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And in great demand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She is currently enjoying great popularity nationwide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- But she seems like someone who's always been popular
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's ever had a "bomby" (poor) period?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have that image
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably nobody here would expect her to have a "poor" image
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's Special Bomby Guest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who played the role of a detective in a TV drama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also this year, she starred in her first musical of the Shakespeare play "Hamlet"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually this guest is also someone who sings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year was her 9th appearance in Kouhaku Uta Gassen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Performing before Fukuyama Masaharu, and after X-Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Without popularity and ability it would be impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to perform at such important positions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been in CMs for major food companies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Job search sites, game consoles, and mobile phones
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's picked up various CMs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When we asked our guests about their impressions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- She is THE "Kokuminteki" (national-level)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my impression
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you know she used to be "bomby" (poor)?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't see it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Neither do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- She seems like a daughter of a rich family
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- A rich kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She is someone who doesn't have a "bomby" impression at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a super popular artist in her 20s
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The place this guest grew up in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the highest production of figs in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The figs are not only put in desserts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But also coated in miso to be eaten as dengaku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The production of succulent plants is also no.1 in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has the highest number of people with surname "Kato"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Aichi prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to reveal the name of the city right now but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Previously, the guest mentioned on Instagram
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm currently at a filming here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And only with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fans rushed to the location causing a large panic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we won't reveal anything more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she is super popular right now but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her house is super "bomby"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When she went to her elementary school friend's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, enjoy the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Waa~ it's luxurious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a meal like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At her own house, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okonomiyaki with nothing but cabbage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- That looks sad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"But, I'll just have to endure it"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason this guest thought that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way back from school at the supermarket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw her mother buying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but clearance and discounted ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The differences with others
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't just limited to food
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take your time and enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa~ It's so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the guest's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Dreary]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that was green was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ja-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty PET bottles reused and repurposed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To grow leftovers of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bean sprouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, we can eat it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Before realising it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The house was filled with edible plants
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- That looks delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Even with just a little green
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to become happy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to support the family
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The guest's mother worked as an aesthetician
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Often coming home late
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, all her classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Played games on the Nintendo DS, which was a hit at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing that distracted the guest from her loneliness was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The brown body pillow she always hugged
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And television
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What she liked the most was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A show with young witch girls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojamajo doremi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to wear cute clothes like this too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yatta!\N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But, they were hand-me-downs from a cousin in the neighbourhood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There were nothing but pants
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like cute one-piece dresses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or pink clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to wear things like that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But that didn't really happen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This guest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was in 5th grade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She experienced an impactful encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the NHK Kouhaku Utagassen on New Year's Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aitakatta, aitakatta, aitakatta, yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on, the guest would perform on the same stage as them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's AKB48!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to be an idol too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"And then if I become famous"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can ease the burden on my mother"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While waiting for her new 6th grade term, there was this night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaasan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be a singer too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I gave up on it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To become an entertainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires a lot of money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as her mother described
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro Namie-san\N(Okinawa Actors School)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Koda Kumi-san\N(Toei Actors School)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfume, and others\N(Actors School Hiroshima)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Artists in the forefront of the industry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them came from talent training schools
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To enter, the admission fee is 300,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesson fees are 20,000 yen per month
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That amounts to 540,000 yen per year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, this requires a lot of money
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- To become an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that it would need that much money
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Two generations yearned to be in the entertainment industry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the money issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, this happened
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- About the training school
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Okaasan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the money...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- It will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make the guest's dream come true
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She did some additional work packaging contact lens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And also did some work delivering bread to homes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all to earn the money to go to the training school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, the guest was able to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,enter a training school in her hometown in Aichi prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To get the stamina necessary to continue with countless hours of intense training
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,During the break times...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Today, I'm having a sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's a chocopan for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, the chocopan looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There were kids who bought various things from convenience stores
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A sandwich, a snack bread
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A juice, and a snack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That amounts to nearly 1000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the guest brought this from home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigiri that her mother makes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have to be grateful to my mother"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I need to work hard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But, she hadn't been able to reach out to any talent agencies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to go for an audition"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"But... they're all in Tokyo"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,”The transportation costs will be high"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,”Going to Tokyo is impossible"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was about to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"If it's this, I can go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In Nagoya, there was a big audition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it will be in Nagoya all the way until the final evaluation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of applicants was 2670
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yoroshiku onegaishimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the final evaluation, among 50 people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The guest who still remained sang this song
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother who wanted to be a singer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Often sang this in karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Koda Kumi's "Anytime"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,3 months after passing the audition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She made her CD debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after, she became very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, the guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here, it's 3000 yen today too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after she turned 20
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never seen her own paycheck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She leaves her salary to her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And receives an allowance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning she would make onigiri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the napkin she's used since elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She would wrap the onigiri and go to work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When she gets home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She would pass time by hugging the brown body pillow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitchen vegetable garden has also continued
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, even the seeds from peppers used in dishes were taken and planted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- If there was anything I'd want to spend money on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be to renovate my grandmother's house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it easier to live in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After achieving success, certain celebrities would immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Live in a large mansion with a garden in the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or buy a luxury car worth over 10 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in the case of our guest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For her grandmother to live easier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She aims to use the money to renovate her grandmother's old house
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, she has appeared in Kouhaku Uta Gassen 9 times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She acts in dramas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She picks up CMs left and right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A super popular artist in her 20s who is active in multiple fields
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already guessed who this guest might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, the image I had of her was completely different
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I take a guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be someone who has international fame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Gaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bean sprouts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which part of that was Lady Gaga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's have our guest appear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- So that's who she was
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Today's Special Bomby Guest is this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's SKE48's Matsui Jurina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yoroshiku onegaishimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's really unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing we're all curious about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still receiving an allowance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my mother manage my income
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's that but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm now over 20, my mother said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's good to at least look at the account book
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Up till then you've never even seen it even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'd never seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many years has it been accumulating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Around 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- So you looked at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, I looked at it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- My reaction was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mmm... I still need to work hard"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was it lower than expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How much money was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- NG!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
